- ğŸŒ **Subdomains Finder**: Identify active subdomains of a target domain.
- ğŸ” **Reverse IP Lookup**: List domains hosted on the same IP.
- ğŸ§° **TXT Toolkit**: Handle text filesâ€”split, clean, remove duplicates, etc.
- ğŸ”“ **Open Port Checker**: Scan for open ports on an IP or domain.
- ğŸ“œ **DNS Records**: Retrieve A, MX, TXT, and other DNS records.
- ğŸ’¡ **Host OSINT**: Gather open-source intelligence on any host.
- ğŸ“– **Help**: Detailed usage instructions for every tool.
- â›” **Exit**: Clean exit from the script.

